title: Day 1 of Big Ten Media Days
description:
Wendi Nix, Tom Luginbill, Desmond Howard and Pete Thamel break down Big Ten Commissioner Kevin Warren's remarks from Day 1 of Big Ten Media Days. Jim Harbaugh, Scott Frost, PJ Fleck and Kirk Ferentz also take the podium.
